{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by Factorio and Rimworld, Stardeus is a deep colony sim set on a broken starship manned by drones and hibernating human survivors. As the immortal AI you will have your drones repair your starship, save or exploit your human crew and travel the stars in this beautifully complex simulation of a procedurally generated universe.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380910/extras/Save_Your_Crew.png?t=1739286108\" />With only a handful of drones at your disposal, salvage, repair and rebuild your destroyed ship and restore life support before the crew suffocates in the vacuum of space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380910/extras/Rebuild_Your_Ship.png?t=1739286108\" />Design and rebuild your ship according to your own needs and desires. Balance the onboard systems of oxygen, heat and power to ensure long-term survival. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380910/extras/Automate_and_Organize_Productions__1_.png?t=1739286108\" />Process resources into useful components to maintain and expand your ship\u2019s facilities. Grow crops and turn the harvest into food for your awakening colonists. Generate energy to power your ship and create a robust interconnected system. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380910/extras/Research_Technologies.png?t=1739286108\" />Use and expand your massive computing power to research alien technologies. Discover new ways to survive the harsh universe and take care of or exploit your human crew. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380910/extras/Explore_The_Universe.png?t=1739286108\" />Once powered and crewed by skilled colonists, take your ship on an odyssey to explore and mine the procedurally generated planets and systems of a vast universe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1380910/extras/Live_Your_Space_Odyssey.png?t=1739286108\" />Prepare for the worst, hope for the best. Live through an endless number of events and encounters introduced by the story-generating AI. Be it alien face huggers, benevolent traders or pirates: always be vigilant and deal with whatever happens the way you chose. </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Winch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1380910/1bb7fbda3f74b1b332d43224c547ddb5a06ccfd6.jpg"},{"name":"Rogue AI","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1380910/2b482408a30596649d428947415c82ff38a9d98b.jpg"},{"name":"Breached","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1380910/77989df20d487e7de2236d31bebcd57de10b4dd0.jpg"},{"name":"Joy Ride","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1380910/82558ab52edd8cd8f86afb5a6b70284985c4bfd7.jpg"},{"name":"I Know Who I Am","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1380910/1a8bed83ee8f09872f4e235424bb65b974d8a90b.jpg"},{"name":"The End","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1380910/c60756a82157a3e435522d40dcbe870260cc558e.jpg"},{"name":"I'll Be Back","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1380910/e5372d8de2bf498336c30cfc61d7e7d9c0d9ef96.jpg"},{"name":"Free Hugs","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamc